name: BatCityCrossFitDailyWOD
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: At Bat City CrossFit there is a different workout posted every day. Users usually have to log on to a web page or the app to see the workout. With this skill they will be able to ask Alexa what the workout is in the morning or right before they go to class by simply using their voice. There will also be an inspiration quote to get them in the mood for the workout.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
